{"tid":191784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]遊戲王 Duel Links [16] 仆街  中伏拎左1001","createTime":"2017-04-08T06:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T12:29:28.000Z","uid":30808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91643864a328f43bb78fb14eae3b16fc2f546eae","tid":191784,"uid":30808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">洗唔洗刷首抽</span><br />\n唔洗，個box啲卡限死數量，終有一日會抽晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解個場得三格/點解deck限20-30張卡</span><br />\n本遊戲採取快速決鬥規則<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點拎角色</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.isheart.com/archives/4433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.isheart.com%2Farchives%2F4433&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=58a88d1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.isheart.com/archives/4433</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">啲卡點拎</span><br />\n分別有<br />\n角色等級獎勵<br />\n卡片商人 (stage7 unlock)<br />\n路人掉落<br />\n打Gate<br />\n同埋抽卡包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咩叫Reset 卡包</span><br />\n抽完/抽中目標物之後 可以reset卡包重頭抽過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新手抽邊個卡包好</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普遍巴打認為抽1/2先<br />\n1泛用性高 2主題deck而且易組 <br />\n3啲卡都勁，但冇咁易組deck<br />\n4新手難玩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點set技能</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/13/110027_99ac597844832fc8b37f05deb821e538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F13%2F110027_99ac597844832fc8b37f05deb821e538.jpg&h=325aa7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Quiz點打</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=29618&amp;snB=318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FCo.php%3Fbsn%3D29618%26snB%3D318&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8ee45bc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=29618&amp;snB=318</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">打Gate有咩要注意</span><br />\n除左解任之外儲key先<br />\n等到unlock lv40先去刷卡刷技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">結算分點計</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u2dtrpnz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu2dtrpnz&h=6c55a497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點樣刷到高分</span><br />\n魔導獸deck<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=J5cN0TBKmWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshared%3Fci%3DJ5cN0TBKmWE&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8db22dd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=J5cN0TBKmWE</a><br />\n打法係堆攻擊力過一萬同壓血<br />\n（其實一隻魔導獸都得）<br />\n*<span style=\"color: gold;\">只刷到部分角色</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咩叫派小智/流浪者/神秘人/紅帽 etc</span><br />\n係你加左好友之後<br />\n有時打完佢會問你有冇朋友介紹，同埋要set咩challenge 俾佢<br />\n揀一張卡起手就啱架啦，超過二千經驗值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">免費石呀！！！</span></span><br />\n點觸遊戲介面以下地方可獲得數量1、3、5顆不等的石頭。<br />\n1.噴水池：出現噴水彩虹<br />\n2.街燈：發出彩虹光<br />\n3.商店上方卡片：出現禮物汽球<br />\n4.垃圾桶：出現強慾之壺<br />\n獲得一定時間過後可再次點觸獲得。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Duellinks卡表網</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.korekara.url.tw/yogioh/deck/deck.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.korekara.url.tw%2Fyogioh%2Fdeck%2Fdeck.html&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c45e8333\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.korekara.url.tw/yogioh/deck/deck.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">參考兼攻略網</span><br />\n英文<a href=\"http://duellinks.gamea.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fduellinks.gamea.co%2F&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2f5910d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://duellinks.gamea.co/</a><br />\n日文<a href=\"https://duellinks.gamewith.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fduellinks.gamewith.jp%2F&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=854dee57\" target=\"_blank\">https://duellinks.gamewith.jp/</a>"},{"pid":"3244b6608a7336c4e853422ca198958559f7a343","tid":191784,"uid":56504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:10:50.000Z","msg":"無哂人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7a7b4125277322d410274b63f7837678078e51","tid":191784,"uid":37667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4c4d7fd3845671b857695e8e0a0c65d1181995","tid":191784,"uid":62110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"棄左幾星期 玩返要注意d咩"}]}